      <title>苏格兰在“无法实现”的 2030 年气候变化目标上倒退</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/scotland-retreats-on-out-of-reach-2030-climate-change-target</link>
      <description><![CDATA[苏格兰政府放弃了到 2030 年将碳排放量减少 75% 的计划，承认该目标无法实现，需要重新调整应对气候变化的方法。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/scotland-retreats-on-out-of-reach-2030-climate-change-target</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:52:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将在北卡罗来纳州筹集 500 万美元以重返赛场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/trump-to-raise-5-million-in-north-carolina-in-return-to-trail</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普(Donald Trump)将于周六在摇摆州北卡罗来纳州举行的一场筹款活动中筹集500万美元，这位共和党候选人在因曼哈顿刑事审判而缺席一周后重返竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/trump-to-raise-5-million-in-north-carolina-in-return-to-trail</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:50:03 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国推动与盟友分享有关选举操纵的情报</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-spurs-intelligence-sharing-with-allies-on-vote-manipulation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士称，随着全球大部分地区今年将参加全国选举，英国正在带头扩大七国集团盟友之外的选举干扰情报共享。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-spurs-intelligence-sharing-with-allies-on-vote-manipulation</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:46:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧尔班的挑战者因涉嫌与外国有联系而成为调查目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/orban-s-sovereignty-protection-agency-targets-his-new-challenger</link>
      <description><![CDATA[匈牙利备受争议的主权保护局在其首批调查之一中将目标瞄准了总理维克多·欧尔班的新政治对手，这引发了人们对该组织将充当执政党工具的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/orban-s-sovereignty-protection-agency-targets-his-new-challenger</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:30:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国部长抨击金融监管机构的多元化提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-minister-blasts-diversity-proposals-by-financial-regulators</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国商务大臣凯米·巴德诺克批评该国监管机构强制金融公司公布员工数据（包括性别和种族）的计划，并警告称这些措施可能会增加成本并抑制增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/uk-minister-blasts-diversity-proposals-by-financial-regulators</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:17:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>公民称肯尼亚国防军司令在直升机坠毁事件中</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/kenya-defence-forces-chief-in-helicopter-crash-citizen-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《公民数字》报道，一架载有肯尼亚国防军司令弗朗西斯·奥戈拉将军的军用直升机在乌干达边境附近的偏远地区坠毁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/kenya-defence-forces-chief-in-helicopter-crash-citizen-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 14:07:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟提议与英国进行谈判以放宽学生和年轻工人的居留条件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/eu-proposes-uk-talks-to-ease-stays-for-students-young-workers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧盟高管希望与英国展开谈判，为年轻人提供一种在有限时间内更便捷地跨越英吉利海峡的方式。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/eu-proposes-uk-talks-to-ease-stays-for-students-young-workers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 13:22:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊朗称以色列的威胁可能引发核政策转变</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-threatens-strike-on-israeli-nuclear-sites-if-it-s-attacked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗表示，如果以色列威胁袭击该国的核设施，伊朗可能会重新审视其核政策，并誓言将对犹太国家的任何此类袭击做出同样的回应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-18/iran-threatens-strike-on-israeli-nuclear-sites-if-it-s-attacked</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 18 Apr 2024 13:08:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
